&lt;li&gt;Strong communication and presentation skills; confident engaging with candidates and senior stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to manage multiple recruiting campaigns under tight deadlines with sharp attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience developing campus strategies, building university partnerships, and supporting early career initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Established network of talent acquisition professionals, university career services and other faculty, and student organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
