&lt;li&gt;Working experience in Python and SQL. Linux/Unix scripting (Perl, bash, etc.) a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional experience with database design is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We support systematic trading in liquid instruments (global equities, futures, and foreign exchange) as well as systematic trading in macro instruments (e.g., bonds, rates, and credit). Candidates with specific work experience and knowledge of market regulations in these areas will be strongly preferred but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
