&lt;li&gt;At least 5 years of professional software engineering experience with a focus on backend system engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience building production data pipelines or data engineering solutions for batch and streaming data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience developing or integrating generative AI and large language model solutions, such as model serving, embedding pipelines, fine-tuning workflows, or production integration with model APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong programming skills in one or more backend languages such as Java, Python, or Go, with demonstrated ability to design maintainable code and services&lt;/li&gt;
