&lt;li&gt;7+ years of mortgage valuation experience covering agency MBS, including specified pools, CMOs, TBA/TBA options, as well as non‑agency products such as RMBS, CMBS, and CLO.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong quantitative or finance background.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of derivatives valuation modeling principles.&lt;/li&gt;
