&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Direct the implementation of Point72’s operational risk framework.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the&amp;nbsp;capture, investigation, and root‑cause analysis&amp;nbsp;of realized events, ensuring effective documentation, remediation planning, and governance reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the&amp;nbsp;analysis, assessment, and continuous monitoring of operational risks&amp;nbsp;across business units, including investment processes, trading operations, technology, and support functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform assessments of new business and critical initiatives to ensure risks are appropriately managed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the enhancement of the firm’s&amp;nbsp;risk frameworks, policies, and standards, promoting a culture of risk awareness and accountability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and present&amp;nbsp;risk reporting&amp;nbsp;for senior management and governance committees.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
