&lt;li&gt;15+ years of professional experience in risk management, auditing, or consulting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Undergraduate degree in accounting, finance, conomics, computer science or engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PRMIA Operational Risk Manager Certificate, FRM, CRISC, CISA, and/or CIA certifications.&lt;/li&gt;
