&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with engineering, infrastructure, security, operations, and business stakeholders to define priorities, surface trade-offs, and drive decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own program execution across multiple workstreams, managing scope, schedule, dependencies, risks, issues, communications, and stakeholder expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare crisp, executive-ready materials that clearly communicate status, risks, decisions needed, and recommend paths forward&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive accountability across teams, ensuring commitments are clear, progress is measurable, and blockers are escalated with urgency and judgment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead infrastructure and platform-related initiatives, which may include server lifecycle, cloud migration, storage modernization, container platforms, resiliency, security remediation, disaster recovery, and operational improvement programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Apply the delivery approach best suited to each initiative, including Agile, Waterfall, or hybrid methods, without adding unnecessary process&lt;/li&gt;
