&lt;h3&gt;What’s required&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree and 5+ years of experience in strategy consulting, digital or technology consulting, program management, technology transformation, or a similarly demanding execution-oriented role&lt;/li&gt;
