&lt;li&gt;Produce clear, actionable daily and monthly P&amp;amp;L variance reports and dashboards tailored for internal stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain robust process controls, reconciliations, and documentation to ensure auditability and reliability of P&amp;amp;L figures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive automation and data quality improvements by developing tools, queries, or workflows that reduce manual effort and increase accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Respond to ad hoc P&amp;amp;L queries from portfolio managers, trading, and investment services with timely, data-backed analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor junior team members and contribute to continuous improvement initiatives that scale the team’s capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
