&lt;li&gt;2-4 years of professional experience in product control, trade operations, or P&amp;amp;L reconciliation at a financial institution or asset manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience performing daily and monthly P&amp;amp;L reconciliations between front office systems and books and records systems across equities, fixed income, and derivatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical skills in Microsoft Excel, including advanced formulas and pivot tables&lt;/li&gt;
