&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using NLP to construct features from varied datasets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Formulating research hypotheses to derive alpha&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and testing the performance of trading signals based on NLP and financial features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Launching identified signals into production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
