&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in computer science, software engineering, mathematics, physics, or a related technical field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 5 years of professional software development experience building production applications, with high proficiency in at least one .NET language (C# or F#) and demonstrated experience working within the .NET ecosystem&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and implementing backend services using ASP.NET Core, including REST API design and server-side pagination models to support large data sets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience building single-page applications in JavaScript and modern front-end libraries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with TypeScript and React and hands-on experience with data grid and charting libraries such as ag-grid and Highcharts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of serialization protocols and authorization/authentication mechanisms and how they impact performance and security&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with relational databases and writing efficient queries against large datasets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to shape product UX and translate user needs into interactive, maintainable front-end designs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills in English and the ability to collaborate across engineering, product, and business teams&lt;/li&gt;
