&lt;li&gt;2-4 years of professional experience in accounting, finance, or financial systems roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-4 years of hands-on experience implementing and supporting Workday Financials, including business process configuration, security model changes, and financial module maintenance&lt;/li&gt;
