&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3–5 years of experience in U.S. taxation, ideally with exposure to partnership taxation and investment funds (private equity, venture capital, hedge funds, or similar)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in accounting or related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with partnership tax concepts, including allocations, capital accounts, investor reporting, and tiered partnership structures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CPA license or concrete roadmap to obtain licensure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of automation initiatives and focus on advancing technology&lt;/li&gt;
