&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Experience in operations, business support, vendor management, administration, project coordination, or analytical roles within a corporate or technology environment.&lt;br&gt;• Strong organizational skills with the ability to manage multiple tasks, priorities, and stakeholders simultaneously while maintaining high attention to detail and execution quality.&lt;br&gt;• Excellent communication, documentation, and relationship-building skills.&lt;br&gt;• Strong analytical mindset and comfort working with data, reporting, and operational metrics.&lt;br&gt;• Ability to work independently and proactively in a fast-paced environment.&lt;br&gt;• Experience working in an international or matrix organization is strongly preferred.&lt;br&gt;• Professional fluency in English (written and spoken) is required.&lt;br&gt;• Strong proficiency with Microsoft Office / Google Workspace tools, especially Excel, PowerPoint, and reporting tools.&lt;br&gt;• Experience with AI-powered productivity tools, Large Language Models, and modern developer-assistance platforms is considered a strong plus, including familiarity with tools such as Cursor, Claude Code, Codex, ChatGPT, and AI-enabled workflow and productivity platforms.&lt;br&gt;• Commitment to the highest ethical standards.&lt;/p&gt;
